00:46:52.190 --> 00:46:55.860
HyperCard, where there were
people developing interactive

00:46:55.860 --> 00:46:59.187
stories in the mid-'80s.

00:46:59.187 --> 00:47:00.520
CAROLYN VANESELTINE: Absolutely.

00:47:00.520 --> 00:47:02.740
And I think part of
what's going on right now

00:47:02.740 --> 00:47:05.740
that makes the change
here is the internet.

00:47:05.740 --> 00:47:08.630
I think how easy
it is for people

00:47:08.630 --> 00:47:11.670
to pass their games from
one person to another,

00:47:11.670 --> 00:47:16.100
because HyperCard, not as easy
